      <title>美国将在袭击以色列后制裁伊朗无人机计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/us-to-sanction-iranian-drone-program-after-attack-on-israel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗周末袭击以色列，威胁将中东推入更广泛的冲突，美国将对伊朗实施新的制裁，目标是该国的导弹和无人机计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/us-to-sanction-iranian-drone-program-after-attack-on-israel</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 23:10:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>参议员卡丁表示，国会领导人正在讨论伊朗石油制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/congressional-leaders-discussing-iran-oil-sanctions-cardin-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议员本·卡丁周二表示，国会领导人正在讨论如何推进对伊朗石油进口商实施制裁的立法，在伊朗直接攻击以色列后，这一问题愈演愈烈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/congressional-leaders-discussing-iran-oil-sanctions-cardin-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 22:06:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中美两国再次就工业产能过剩问题发生争执</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/us-and-china-continue-to-spar-over-overcapacity-claims</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国向中国重申其对世界第二大经济体工业产能过剩的担忧，促使北京官员反驳这一指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/us-and-china-continue-to-spar-over-overcapacity-claims</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 21:12:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列袭击后伊朗外交官访问联合国激起美国焦虑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/iranian-diplomat-s-un-visit-stirs-us-angst-after-israel-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗周末对以色列的袭击使伊斯兰共和国外交部长周四访问纽约参加联合国会议的计划变得更加复杂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/iranian-diplomat-s-un-visit-stirs-us-angst-after-israel-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 21:05:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国威胁实施战争制裁，中国对俄罗斯出口大幅下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/china-s-exports-to-russia-slump-amid-us-threat-of-war-sanctions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[3月份，中国对俄罗斯的出口大幅下滑，这是自2022年中期以来的首次同比下降，原因是美国越来越多地威胁称，如果中国的商品帮助莫斯科入侵乌克兰，就会对北京进行报复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/china-s-exports-to-russia-slump-amid-us-threat-of-war-sanctions</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
