    <item>
      <title>杰里米·亨特表示降息将提振英国情绪，暗示秋季投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/hunt-says-rate-cuts-would-lift-uk-mood-hints-at-fall-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣杰里米·亨特表示，今年晚些时候降息的前景将提振选民的情绪，并暗示首相苏纳克要到秋季才会举行大选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/hunt-says-rate-cuts-would-lift-uk-mood-hints-at-fall-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 18:38:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟报告支持电信整合和强劲的能源市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/eu-report-calls-for-telecom-consolidation-strong-energy-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据欧盟委托编写的一份关于竞争力的报告，欧盟应考虑对电信运营商进行整合，以此作为改善欧盟移动和固定网络的一种方式，并应进一步整合其能源市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/eu-report-calls-for-telecom-consolidation-strong-energy-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 16:24:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新西兰总理表示财政紧缩是抑制物价、刺激经济增长的关键</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/nz-pm-says-fiscal-restraint-key-to-taming-prices-stoking-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰总理克里斯托弗·卢克森(Christopher Luxon)在发布其政府第一份财政蓝图前几周表示，新西兰需要检查政府支出，以成功抑制通货膨胀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/nz-pm-says-fiscal-restraint-key-to-taming-prices-stoking-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 09:35:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
